DRUGF.original: Some bikers are escaping by boat. There are boats moored around the shoreline should you need them.
DRUGF.translated: 有些飞车党正用船逃跑，你应该需要那些停泊在岸边的船。

DRUGF.original: Take a look around. Find the deal.
DRUGF.translated: 四处查看，找出交易地点。

DRUGF.original: Collect all of the ~G~drugs~S~ the targets drop.
DRUGF.translated: 收集目标掉下的所有~G~毒品~S~。

DRUGF.original: You've found the deal. The ~r~targets~s~ are spread over every floor of this building. Work your way up, clear them out.
DRUGF.translated: 你找到了交易地点，~r~目标~s~分散在大楼的各个楼层。用你的方法干掉他们。

DRUGF.original: Wait here for the rest of your crew to arrive.
DRUGF.translated: 在这里等待你的伙伴们到达。

DRUGF.original: You've taken the drugs and eliminated the witnesses. Get to the ~Y~rendezvous point.~S~
DRUGF.translated: 你已经拿到毒品并消灭了目击者，前往~Y~会合地点。~S~

DRUGF.original: The remaining ~R~Angels of Death~S~ are fleeing. Eliminate them.
DRUGF.translated: 剩余的~R~Angels of Death~S~正在逃跑，消灭他们。
